{"tid":2347901,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"流亡英國香港學生劉康　中銀戶口被終止　涉款HK$47.23","createTime":"2020-12-31T11:05:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-31T11:17:24.000Z","uid":261647,"like":6,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"31527ce51870d79a5687f381affd521f3680ca03","tid":2347901,"uid":261647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T11:05:59.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/cantonese.rfa/posts/4835342476540232\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fcantonese.rfa%2Fposts%2F4835342476540232&d=BLGvZshAgiFYydKSMDjJm5KGII16X6EVRppoT8yKAsg%3D&h=09340f88\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/cantonese.rfa/posts/4835342476540232</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6hOLxeK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6hOLxeK.jpg&h=4b62ce7c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【流亡英國香港學生劉康】<br />\n【中銀戶口被終止 涉款HKD$47.23】<br />\n<br />\n被香港警察以涉嫌違反《港區國安法》通緝、早前已流亡英國的香港學生劉康表示，其銀行戶口在12月24日遭中銀終止，該戶口有約五十元港幣（HKD$47.23）。<br />\n<br />\n劉康表示，這證明香港政府和中國政府會為打壓異見而侵犯香港人的私人財產，批評中共已使香港私人財產得不到保障，損害香港金融中心聲譽，呼籲世界各國制裁中銀、其他中共控制的中資銀行和香港政府。"},{"pid":"802f9251d43689998764edefe5126fb1a3109731","tid":2347901,"uid":41368,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T11:07:04.000Z","msg":"痴線 咁多錢 一定係洗黑錢啦"},{"pid":"0de80e5d97bd78b32ec072a2255eb5471e5809b2","tid":2347901,"uid":284432,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T11:08:45.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e398fb72f770c7c4ec3d32e12f3d59df0347deef","tid":2347901,"uid":132986,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T11:10:38.000Z","msg":"開始制裁啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n驚到瀨屎"},{"pid":"5637c9bb51c00143f994106e51973b02e09aca94","tid":2347901,"uid":39277,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"r